snippet.title: VR Game Trailer 🔪 StabitVR.com 🔪 CUT to the PRANK ⚔️ Record your grandma playing 🎥
snippet.description:
What's bigger than VR? Videos of people in VR doing funny sh!t 🔪StabitVR.com🔪 is the VR game you want your friend, dad, or grandma to play while recording them for a laugh 🎥

PLAY NOW on Steam  🔗 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2908000/Stab_It_VRcom/
AND on Meta Quest 🔗 https://www.meta.com/experiences/8100375746645564/

🎁 Meta Quest 3 GIVEAWAY! 🎁

We're giving away a Meta Quest 3 headset in 30 days ⏳

TO ENTER:
✅ DOWNLOAD Stab It VR on Meta Quest here: 🔗https://www.meta.com/experiences/8100375746645564/
✅ SHOOT A VIDEO of your friend/dad/grandma playing
✅ UPLOAD THE VIDEO on YouTube with "www.StabitVR.com" in your description + ADD TO THIS PLAYLIST: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLgsEeD9QFEA7fWHrALCo_kJ7HVQgKI5W4&si=wk9zWvPB2k8CC7Qn

🏆 MOST LIKED VIDEO WINS!
⏳ Contest ends May 9, 2024
👀 Winner announced in comments
